quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,Nuun; Mede Twerεdua ne Adeε a wͻ’de (Twerεdua no) twerε no di nse sε
  68,2,"(Nkͻmhyεni), wommͻͻ dam wͻwo Wura Nyankopͻn adom no ho"
  68,3,"Nokorε nso sε, wowͻ akatua a, εtoͻ nntwa da"
  68,4,"Nokorε nso sε, wowͻ suban pa a εkorͻn paa so"
  68,5,"Enti wobehunu, na wͻn nso behunu"
  68,6,Momu nea w’abͻ dam
  68,7,"Nokorε sε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn na Onim obi a w’ayera afri Ne kwan no soͻ, Ɔno ara nso na Onim ateneneefoͻ no"
  68,8,Enti entie wͻn a wͻ’fa nokorԑ no atorᴐsԑm no
  68,9,"Wͻ’pεsε, anka wogo woho (ma wͻn), na wͻnso ayε bͻkͻͻ (ama wo)"
  68,10,Entie obi a odi nse hunu bebrebe biara
  68,11,"(Obi a) ͻka nkyisεm, nsekubͻni a ͻde (nkorͻfoͻ ho) nsεm nenam"
  68,12,"(Obi a) osi papayε ho kwan, mmratofoͻ, bͻneyεfoͻ no"
  68,13,"Otrimuͻdenfoͻ a bͻne nkͻmra nyinaa ͻwͻ mu bie, εno akyi nso ͻbͻ ntεtε-busua"
  68,14,Efirisε ͻwͻ sika ne mma (pii) nti
  68,15,"Sε yεrekenkan Yεn Nsεm kyerε no a, deɛ ɔka ne sɛ, tetefoͻ no anansesεm"
  68,16,Yε’bεhyε no nnso wͻ ne hwene so
  68,17,"Nokorε sε, Y’asͻ (Makafoͻ no) ahwε sεdeε Yε’sͻͻ Afuo wurafoͻ no hwεeε no, εberε a wͻ’kaa ntam sε, wͻ’bεte afuo no mu nnͻbae no anͻpa tutuutu no"
  68,18,"W’annka sε, (In Shaa’a-Laah) sε Nyankopͻn pε a"
  68,19,"Enti mmusuo bi fri wo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ betwaa (afuo no) ho hyiae (hyee no pasaa) wͻ εberε a, na wͻn adeda"
  68,20,Adeε kyeeε no na (afuo no ahye) ayε tumm a hwee nni (asaase no) soͻ
  68,21,Adeε kyee anͻpa tutuutu no wͻ’frεfrεε wͻn ho (kaa sε)
  68,22,"“Sε mobεte momfudeε no a, εneε monkͻ moafuo no mu anͻpa tutuutu”"
  68,23,Enti wͻ’sii mu kͻe; na wͻ’berεε wͻn nne ase (kaa sε)
  68,24,“Momma ohiani biara nnwura (afuo yi) mu mma moha nnε “
  68,25,"Anͻpa no, wͻ’de wͻn adwen (bͻne) no sii mu kͻͻ (afuo no mu) wͻ tumi so"
  68,26,"Ɛberε a wͻ’hunuu (afuo) no, wͻ’kaa sε: “Nokorε sε, yayera (kwan no)“"
  68,27,"Daabi, (εnyε kwan na ya yayera, na mmom ya’dwen bͻne nti) ahwere yεn"
  68,28,"Wͻn mu nnipa papa no (anaasε wͻn mu adantamu no) kaa sε: “M’annka ankyerε mo sε, adεn na mo mmͻ (Nyankopͻn) abodin?”"
  68,29,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Kronkron Hene ne ye’ Wura Nyankopͻn. Nokorε sε, ya’yε bͻne”"
  68,30,Afei wͻ’danee wͻn ho hwεε wͻn ho wͻn ho anim bᴐᴐ wͻn ho soboᴐ
  68,31,"Wͻ’kaa sε: Ao, adi ayε yεn. Nokorε sε y’ayε bͻne paa"
  68,32,"Ebia ye’ Wura Nyankopͻn de deε εyε kyεn no bεhyε yεn anan mu. Nokorε sε, ye’Wura Nyankopͻn na yɛde ya’ni to no soɔ“"
  68,33,"Saa ara na Wiase asotwee no teε, nokorε sε, Daakye asotwee no deε εso paa, sε anka wcnim a"